Predicate-substrate for the FKLW density theorem: given a UNITARY
representation ПҒ : BraidGroup n вҶ’ SU(d) whose image's Lie algebra spans
a target Lie subalgebra рқ”Ө вҠҶ рқ”І(d), the closure of ПҒ(BraidGroup n) is dense
